  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK720">
<l>aṅkaṇattu ḷukka vamiḻtaṟṟāṟ ṟaṅkaṇatta</l>
<l>rallārmuṟ kōṭṭi koḷal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To utter (a good word) in the assembly of those who are of inferior rank is like dropping nectar on the ground.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
